high_descs: Turn and walk to the shelf, hang a right, and go to the island counter.
Pick up the plate to the right of the wine bottle.
Take the plate to the fridge across the room.
Chill the plate in the fridge.
Take the chilled plate across the room to the shelves in the corner.
Put the chilled plate on the middle shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled plate on the middle shelf in the corner.

high_descs: Move to side of kitchen island opposite of the fridge.
Move to the fridge to the right of the sink across the island.
Open fridge, place plate inside on bottom shelf, let plate chill for a few moments before retrieving the plate and closing the door again.
Move to wooden shelf across from the bin on the other side of the island.
Place the plate on the bottom shelf of the wooden shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled plate on the wooden shelf.

high_descs: Turn left, go the brown shelves, turn right, and go to the white counter.
Take a gray plate from the white counter.
Turn left, go to the white dishwasher, turn right, and go to the refrigerator.

Open the refrigerator, place the gray plate in the refrigerator, close the refrigerator, wait three seconds, open the refrigerator, take the gray plate from the refrigerator, and close the refrigerator.
Turn around, go to the oven, turn left, turn right, turn left, and go to the brown shelves.
Put the gray plate on the brown shelves.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled gray plate on the brown shelves.
